    "content": "To clone or download this application from Github, go to the main page of this repository and then click Clone button to clone this repository or download as zip file. This content can also be downloaded using content manager by following these instructions. Path of the application within the repository is usb_apps_device/apps/hid_keyboard. Following table gives the details of project configurations, target device used, hardware and its IDE. Open the project using the respective IDE and build it. | Project Name | IDE | Target Device | Hardware / Configuration | . | sam_e70_xult.X | MPLABX | ATSAME70Q21B | SAM E70 Xplained Ultra Board | . | sam_e70_xult_freertos.X | MPLABX | ATSAME70Q21B | SAM E70 Xplained Ultra Board | . ",
